chapters.title: How do we care for our agents
Whats it like being an organization that focuses on resources and service
What have folks been texting in about

description:
#GamesHotline staff members Anita Sarkeesian and Jae Lin talk about running the Hotline for a year. In this segment from the livestream over on Twitch, they covered the changes we've made, building in accountability support, and expanding our hours.



Learn more at: gameshotline.org
Blog: https://gameshotline.org/blog/
Follow us on Twitch: twitch.tv/femfreq
